Class AdminService

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.business.AdminService
All Implemented Interfaces:
adminInterface
public class AdminService extends Object implements adminInterface
The AdminService class provides the business logic for all administrative tasks. It interacts with various DAO classes to perform operations such as approving gym requests, viewing users, and deleting entities.
